Melt oil over medium heat. Saute onion in oil until translucent. Add green chilies and diced tomatoes. Cook, stirring constantly until about half the liquid evaporates. Add cream cheese and cook until melted, 3 to 5 minutes. Stir constantly. Stir in Swanson(R) Unsalted Chicken Broth, cream, and lemon juice. Season with garlic powder, salt, cumin, onion salt, and cayenne. Add shredded chicken and heat until warmed through. Garnish each serving with chopped green onions, chopped cilantro, and crushed tortilla chips.